in no uncertain terms!

729
00:56:00,280 --> 00:56:03,955
- Were you very big?.
- Oh, yes.

730
00:56:05,000 --> 00:56:06,956
How big?.

731
00:56:07,040 --> 00:56:11,272
When I barked... I was enormous.

732
00:56:13,400 --> 00:56:18,474
