739
00:56:45,440 --> 00:56:50,912
Yes, this, erm... this business of smell
is very interesting, isn't it?.

740
00:56:51,000 --> 00:56:53,195
Interesting.

741
00:56:53,280 --> 00:56:56,192
If there's one thing
I could find fault with the Master,

742
00:56:56,280 --> 00:56:58,316
