747
00:57:14,080 --> 00:57:16,753
No, most apposite.

748
00:57:16,840 --> 00:57:21,391
I believe I have thought
exactly the same thing.

749
00:57:23,640 --> 00:57:26,029
What sort of a dog were you, anyway?.

750
00:57:27,840 --> 00:57:29,796
I beg your pardon?.

751
00:57:29,880 --> 00:57:31,996
I mean in your day.

752
00:57:32,080 --> 00:57:34,469
You know, before you took...

753
00:57:34,560 --> 00:57:36,790
holy orders.

754
00:57:36,880 --> 00:57:39,713
