755
00:57:58,920 --> 00:58:01,115
Quite a session. Damn good value.

756
00:58:01,200 --> 00:58:04,317
Listen, I've been thinking.
This is getting out of hand.

757
00:58:05,760 --> 00:58:07,990
The man is clearly
suffering from delusions.

758
00:58:08,080 --> 00:58:10,116
And as for the Tokay...

759
00:58:10,200 --> 00:58:12,919
