I never develop a taste for it.

760
00:58:13,000 --> 00:58:15,992
It's hard to find
and devilishly expensive.

761
00:58:16,080 --> 00:58:19,834
Ten guineas to hear a dean say
he believed he was once a dog!

762
00:58:19,920 --> 00:58:21,911
I must be mad.

763
00:58:22,000 --> 00:58:23,991
- Good as gold.
- Shh.

764
00:58:24,080 --> 00:58:27,755
I don't want your money.
This has gone too far.

765
00:58:27,840 --> 00:58:32,595
- But you can't stop now, young Fisk.
- Well, I see no point in continuing.

766
00:58:32,680 --> 00:58:37,310
The man believes what he believes.
That's that.

767
00:58:43,880 --> 00:58:47,589
You're not one of these blokes
