a bottle of the elixir for free?.

770
00:58:58,480 --> 00:59:00,198
For free?.

771
00:59:08,760 --> 00:59:12,833
This bloke owes me. He owes me more
than one favour too, I'II tell you that.

772
00:59:12,920 --> 00:59:17,948
And if anyone's got a bottle or two,
His Nawabship will.

773
00:59:21,960 --> 00:59:24,554
Tokay, you say?. An Imperial?.

774
00:59:24,640 --> 00:59:27,598
- We're finding it hard to come by.
- I should jolly well think so.

775
00:59:27,680 --> 00:59:31,116
Rather extravagant
being so keen on it, I'd say.

776
00:59:31,200 --> 00:59:33,270
- You must be quite the connoisseur.
- It's not for him.

777
00:59:33,360 --> 00:59:35,954
It's for Dean Spanley.

778
00:59:36,040 --> 00:59:39,430
For Spanley?.
OId Wag Spanley Iikes Tokay?.

779
00:59:39,520 --> 00:59:42,717
