01:08:55,120 --> 01:08:59,511
Who, in God's name, called you what?.

923
01:08:59,600 --> 01:09:03,593
The Master. He called me Wag.

924
01:09:04,800 --> 01:09:08,315
For reasons I never understood. Wag.

925
01:09:09,680 --> 01:09:11,671
But that was
the greatness of the Master,

926
01:09:11,760 --> 01:09:15,070
